<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ nǐ shì wǒ zuì zhī xīn de péng yǒu zhǔ nǐ shì wǒ zuì qīn ài de bàn lǚ.
 wǒ de xīn zài tiān tiān zhuī xiǎng zhe nǐ kě wàng jiàn dào nǐ de miàn.
 zài wǒ rén shēng de měi yī gè tái jiē zài wǒ rén shēng de měi yī gè xiǎo zhàn,
 nǐ de shǒu zǒng shì zài chān lā zhe wǒ, bǎ wǒ dài zài nǐ shēn biān,
 gào sù wǒ dāng zǒu de lù, méi yǒu huá xiàng sǐ wáng xiàn.
 nǐ ài hé děng de zhǎng kuò shēn gāo, wǒ xīn fā chū jīng tàn.
 yǒu le zhǔ hái yào shén me! wǒ xīn yǔ zhǔ xīn xiāng lián,
 wǒ yǐ qǐ shì yào gēn suí zhǔ yǒng bù gǎi biàn.</lyrics>
<title>zuì zhī xīn de péng yǒu 迦南34</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>34</hymn_number>
</song>